{"tid":1660734,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[行動] 口罩文宣","createTime":"2019-10-17T16:25:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T16:29:42.000Z","uid":159353,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b5d3a73b3792d23e642d69d5ce841281f611c6d8","tid":1660734,"uid":159353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T16:25:34.000Z","msg":"為咗係1020九龍大遊行重現200萬人，連登巴絲一直諗宣傳方法打破<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">同溫層</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，將1020大遊行傳遍香港。小弟忽發奇想，諗到同<span style=\"color: brown;\">流動連儂牆</span>一樣嘅人體文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣口罩</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qRdDBGA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqRdDBGA.jpg&h=c34622eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就係用筆寫低10&middot;20係口罩上邊。咁巴絲每日戴口罩出街嗰時都可以俾市民睇到10&middot;20 四個數字，將1020大遊行嘅消息傳遍街頭 (出一次街幾百人睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)。畫兩畫就做到文宣又方便。<br />\n<br />\n仲有連登巴絲多才藝，發揮小宇宙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，設計唔同嘅10&middot;20 文宣口罩。<br />\n<br />\n我鍾意戴黑口罩喎，咁用雙面膠砌字/白色筆寫啦。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5svOed4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5svOed4.jpg&h=c4f4056d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲可以係白紙上邊寫完再黏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E9vyqu2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE9vyqu2.jpg&h=3a07bedd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最懶嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，唔用marker筆，直接用原子筆寫上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(小弟初稿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0SPjk3v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0SPjk3v.jpg&h=90aca4e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴絲快啲發揮創意將普通嘅口罩變成文宣工具<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，同全香港人講10&middot;20 大遊行啊。<br />\n<br />\n係呢幾日，我要將香港街道變成<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">連儂街</span></span>，我地嘅口罩就係當中嘅<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">流動memo 紙</span></span>，將10&middot;20大遊行帶到香港每一個角落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1020<br />\n九龍見</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"437871fa3d30dec216e39a5113e0a5bf6347e477","tid":1660734,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T16:25:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W04Z2Gp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW04Z2Gp.jpg&h=e79a1d2a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"e35deb2ac5745b5f7bd195caf0f5b7ab5b4d01d9","tid":1660734,"uid":272292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T16:26:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bbf76df0216bc5c7f4ab9c2e53cc24c304953f9d","tid":1660734,"uid":159353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T16:29:42.000Z","msg":"推1"}]}